    'ib_prcode' : str(randrange(10000,100000,1)),
    'ib_cf_qty' : str(randrange(-10,1000,1)),
    'new_ib_vs_stock_cv' : str(randrange(-10,1000,1))
  }).to_dict() for _ in range(numberOfRows)]
